
Changes in version 3.0c since v3.0 include:
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ
* A new priority setting was added to System.aml. This setting allows
  you to adjust the amount of cpu time yielded to the operating system
  in multitasking environments such Windows or OS/2. The default setting
  now yields the maximum amount of time to the operating system.

* New Macros:
  ù Status    - Custom status line example
  ù Vcursor   - Vertical cursor line
  ù Zapem     - Shoot'em-up game

* Bug fixes, including fixes for various problems with editing very
  large files.

(see Whatsnew.doc for new features in v3.0 since v2.1a)
